Description
-----------

Creates a [specular map](Texturing "Texturing") stage in a material
shader.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    specularmap [map]

Parameters
----------

-   [map] - the relative path and file name from base to the specified
    specular map image.

Notes
-----

This keyword is shorthand for...

    {
     blend specularmap
     map [map]
    }

